{"tid":1385792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實學生真正需要係發完夢之後餐飯","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:11.000Z","uid":200604,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b33258153ca85828d3fa3989b3ab7ebd8140b99","tid":1385792,"uid":200604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"帶定頭盔: 唔係要求多多嘅港孩 <br />\n只係想表達下我嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n佢地真正需要係發完夢之後嘅個餐飯<br />\n忙完一整日 去到夜晚好多店都關咗 已經無乜選擇<br />\n其實學生唔係窮到完全連十幾蚊嘅野都買唔起<br />\n而係佢地買唔起貴野 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例如m記 佢地寧願買一個包$10 都唔會買一個$30嘅餐</span><br />\n佢地更加食唔起大排檔<br />\n所以你地唔好當佢地係難民 完全無野落肚<br />\n你地依架話買包比佢地 同佢地平時食開有乜野分別？ <br />\n<br />\n另外 依班學生發緊夢個陣根本無心情食野<br />\n有人建議話買西餅、香蕉<br />\n無錯 的確係提供到能量 亦唔易變壞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但麻煩你地諗清楚佢地真正需要啲咩</span><br />\n幾蚊一條蕉佢地自己都買得起啦<br />\n户口得翻四百蚊 所以唔敢每餐食多過$20嘅野咁計<br />\n如果你地真係有心想支持佢地 <br />\n乜唔係應該係佢地忙完一整日之後<br />\n請佢地坐低食一餐熱嘅飯咩？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我都唔知啲學生幾耐無食餐會飽嘅正餐</span><br />\n<br />\n已經唔係質素嘅問題 就算純粹想飽肚<br />\n香港地是但搵碗麵都講緊接近$40<br />\n翻part time 一個鐘先得$45<br />\n我真係寧願食個m 記包算<br />\n<br />\n利申學生 覺得譚仔依類麵鋪對我依啲基層學生嚟講貴 平時唔敢加野飲 只會嗌一餸"},{"pid":"ab94bac9f7b8a1d66e268ae5c7d0155aa18587c4","tid":1385792,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"e72a93524ba06337dc147f242198ef38e00dee94","tid":1385792,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b521217cb34abab162770d70730c32fa7f7f47","tid":1385792,"uid":200604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e72a93524ba06337dc147f242198ef38e00dee94","tid":1385792,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"a21fb2c24370d06aae65578b7f7d837fe23bf5ce","tid":1385792,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b521217cb34abab162770d70730c32fa7f7f47","tid":1385792,"uid":200604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e72a93524ba06337dc147f242198ef38e00dee94","tid":1385792,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:11.000Z","msg":"你個名睇到我 孛力 走已 口左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}